name: Qrung the Quake
description:
Qrung is an AntiMetro; Meta creatures developed by Khuzard of the future to save the earth by decimating human civilization.

The Quake destroys skyscrapers and concrete structures by vibrating its horns and one-eyed halo.

This is objkt is a part of Monday Art Club internal program; PFP entry for Smir138.
